星期都考考到而家都仲考緊)<br />\n4. 我BOOK唔到D堂, 我而家來排WAITING。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}